<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Métodos de Entrega — Marketplace</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
  <main class="container">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
      <a href="/supermarket/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">← Voltar</a>
      <h1 class="page-title" style="margin:0">Métodos de Entrega</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="max-width:640px">
      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-error" style="margin-bottom:1.25rem">⚠ <%= error %></div>
      <% } %>
      <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-success" style="margin-bottom:1.25rem">✔ <%= success %></div>
      <% } %>

      <p style="color:var(--text-2);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
        Define que métodos de entrega disponibilizas aos clientes e o respetivo custo.
        Tens de ativar pelo menos um método.
      </p>

      <form action="/supermarket/delivery" method="POST" novalidate>

        <!-- Levantamento em loja -->
        <div class="card" style="background:var(--bg-3);margin-bottom:1.25rem">
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:1rem">
            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;cursor:pointer">
              <input type="checkbox" name="pickupEnabled" id="pickupEnabled"
                     style="width:auto;margin:0"
                     <%= current.pickup.enabled ? 'checked' : '' %>>
              <span style="font-weight:600">🏪 Levantamento em loja</span>
            </label>
            <p style="color:var(--text-3);font-size:.825rem;margin:.4rem 0 0 1.85rem">
              O cliente vai buscar a encomenda à loja.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" style="margin:0 0 0 1.85rem">
            <label for="pickupCost">Custo (€)</label>
            <input type="number" id="pickupCost" name="pickupCost"
                   step="0.01" min="0"
                   value="<%= current.pickup.cost %>"
                   style="max-width:160px">
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Entrega por estafeta -->
        <div class="card" style="background:var(--bg-3);margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:1rem">
            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;cursor:pointer">
              <input type="checkbox" name="courierEnabled" id="courierEnabled"
                     style="width:auto;margin:0"
                     <%= current.courier.enabled ? 'checked' : '' %>>
              <span style="font-weight:600">🛵 Entrega por estafeta</span>
            </label>
            <p style="color:var(--text-3);font-size:.825rem;margin:.4rem 0 0 1.85rem">
              Um estafeta entrega a encomenda ao domicílio do cliente.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" style="margin:0 0 0 1.85rem">
            <label for="courierCost">Custo (€)</label>
            <input type="number" id="courierCost" name="courierCost"
                   step="0.01" min="0"
                   value="<%= current.courier.cost %>"
                   style="max-width:160px">
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Guardar alterações</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
